# Agent Configuration Structure

## Requirements

- [!] [Project Name] AGENTS.md provides AI agents with project methodology context following context tree convention
  - **Context tree pattern**: Root AGENTS.md + ctxt/ sub-agents (see `.livespec/standard/conventions/context-tree.spec.md`)
