  - **Benefits**: Specialized contexts, proactive loading, improved focus efficiency

- [!] [Project Name] AGENTS.md content generated from project specifications
  - **Sources**: PURPOSE.md, workspace/*.spec.md, requirements, strategy
  - **Content structure**: Optimized for context positioning (START/MIDDLE/END) per `.livespec/guides/context-positioning.md`
  - **Compression**: Level declared in workspace/constitution.spec.md frontmatter
  - **No frontmatter**: Clean context for agents (convention requirement)
  - **Inline edit warning**: Instructs regeneration

- [!] [Project Name] AGENTS.md uses START/MIDDLE/END positioning for optimal agent processing
  - **START section (30-40%)**: Core principles, critical warnings, essential protocols
  - **MIDDLE section (40%)**: Quick start, methodology overview, reference library
  - **END section (20-30%)**: Prompts registry, current priorities
  - **Rationale**: Exploits primacy and recency bias per research

