- AGENTS.md generated from project sources (PURPOSE.md, workspace specs)
- Content structure follows START/MIDDLE/END positioning
- Compression level applied per constitution.spec.md
- No frontmatter (clean context per convention)
- Inline edit warning at top
- File size within convention budgets (20-30KB for root)
- Regeneration workflow documented and functional
- Agent can guide users through project methodology
